  "contentHtml": "<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"font-size:14px;text-wrap-mode:wrap;line-height:40px;text-align:center;\"><span style=\"font-size:29px;\">关于推荐</span><span style=\"font-size:29px;\">陈艳华</span><span style=\"font-size:29px;\">同志</span><span style=\"font-size:29px;\">申报2025年度</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"font-size:14px;text-wrap-mode:wrap;line-height:40px;text-align:center;\"><span style=\"font-size:29px;\">校优秀教育工作者</span><span style=\"font-size:29px;\">的公示</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:40px;\"><span style=\"font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px;\"><span style=\"font-family:仿宋;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:40px;\"><span style=\"font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px;\"><span style=\"font-family:仿宋;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;根据《福建中医药大学教职工表彰评选办法》（闽中医人〔</span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋;\">2025〕38号）《福建中医药大学教职工评优评先评奖管理规定暂行办法》（闽中医办〔2021〕11号）</span></span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px;\">和学校有关通知，经个人申请、材料初审、我处</span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px;\">考核小组</span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px;\">投票表决通过，拟推荐</span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px;\">陈艳华</span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px;\">同志申报</span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px;\">2025年度校优秀教育工作者</span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px;\">。现予公示。</span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px;\"><br /></span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px;\"><span style=\"font-family:仿宋;\">公示时间：</span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋;\">202</span></span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px;\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px;\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px;\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px;\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px;\">24</span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px;\"><span style=\"font-family:仿宋;\"